{
  "texts": [
    "The OECD database requires roughly 85GB of storage and the voting records requires 1GB of storage.",
    "Our implementation is based on PyTorch and Hugging Face's \"transformers\" and \"sentencetransformers\" libraries.",
    "A full list of dependencies and their versions is provided in our public repository.",
    "GitHub Copilot was used in the development of some of our code to assist with boilerplate functions and standard NLP preprocessing tasks.",
    "All source code and dataset annotations are released under the MIT License."
  ]
}